des: Dry Cleaning and Laundry becomes easier with pickup and delivery dry cleaning and laundry services. Just say 'Alexa, launch Collins Cleaners' to get started! Now you can tell Collins Cleaners you are on your way so they can have your clothes ready by the time you get there! Just say: 1. 'Alexa, open Collins Cleaners' 2. 'I am on my way'
